summary: An ordinance amending Section 2 of Ordinance No. 34501, entitled: "An ordinance authorizing and directing the Board of Public Works and City Engineer to construct a 24-inch water main through the siphon tunnel at Third Avenue West and from the south shaft of said tunnel at Third Avenue West and Nickerson Street, and from the north shaft of said tunnel to Second Avenue Northwest and West Thirty-ninth Street, and appropriating money the money to pay the cost thereof', approved March 24, 1915.
